LatexCommand label
name "subsec:Conversion-to-tensor"

\end_inset

Conversion to tensor product form
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
A (rational or non-rational) S-patch of depth 
\begin_inset Formula $d$
\end_inset

 has the tensor product Bézier patch form
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\hat{S}(u,v)=\sum_{i=0}^{d}\sum_{j=0}^{d}C_{ij}B_{i}^{d}(u)B_{j}^{d}(v)
\end{equation}

\end_inset

with the control points
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
C_{ij}=\sum_{\substack{\mathbf{s}\\
s_{2}+s_{3}=i\\
s_{3}+s_{4}=j
}
}\frac{\binom{d}{\mathbf{s}}}{\binom{d}{i}\binom{d}{j}}P_{\mathbf{s}}.
\end{equation}

\end_inset


